// Function to generate a random word from VALID_WORDS
const generateRandomWord = () => {
  const randomIndex = Math.floor(Math.random() * VALID_WORDS.length);
  return VALID_WORDS[randomIndex];
};

// Function to generate the word set for the game
const generateWordSet = () => {
  const word = generateRandomWord();
  const wordSet = Array.from({ length: 5 }, () => word);
  return wordSet;
};
